                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17790915-54-defend538 t17790915-54-punish277"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. DEPUTY RECORDER.</p>
               <p>The prisoner was humbly recommended, by both the Prosecutor and the Jury, to his Majesty's Mercy.</p>
